ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectHiawatha First Nation (ON) SETTING APART
PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the HIAWATHA FIRST NATION, of 77.75 hectares (192.1 acres) of land, including mines and minerals, in the Township of Otonabee-South Monaghan, Ontario, as an addition to Hiawatha First Nation Reserve No. 36
